00:29 <xwikiorg\_guest\_7> Hey there! I have a strange issue with some spaces here. I can not figure out how to delete them. After doing researches for some hours now I am logged in as Superadmin now ... I see the spaces in the Documents Tree view and after 'deleting' them they are still at the xwiki menus. After klicking on them there is a message, that the page does not exist and I am suggested to create the page. Has anyone a solution for me?
